title: Amiga Paula does XM: TNK - Age Of Analogia (A1200🎧Dolbyfied)
description:
"Age Of Analogia" (1998) by TNK/Rlt^DZone^Caffein (Philippe Meisburger). Art "Fairyland" (1996) by Lazur/TRSI^Anadune^Nah-Kolor.

Made using real A1200 Rev. 1D.4 audio. Playback from DeliTracker 2.34 with 14Bit-NotePlayer 4.30:
